Oat: Anything to confess to me?
Are you lying?

01:27:54.120 --> 01:27:55.640
Nantanan: I’ve been with you
for a whole day.

01:27:55.640 --> 01:27:57.470
Nantanan: I let you win every game.

01:27:57.470 --> 01:28:00.000
Nantanan: I told you every clue.

01:28:00.550 --> 01:28:01.320
Nantanan: How would I lie...

01:28:01.320 --> 01:28:02.900
Oat: But you are an actress.
I can trust you, right?

01:28:02.900 --> 01:28:04.280
Nantanan: You're an actor too.

01:28:04.280 --> 01:28:05.440
[That's right.]

01:28:05.440 --> 01:28:06.700
Oat: Okay. I trust you.

01:28:06.720 --> 01:28:08.290
Oat: I'll protect you.

01:28:11.960 --> 01:28:14.080
[Seeing Oat.]

01:28:17.550 --> 01:28:18.480
Jeff: Up there.

01:28:18.800 --> 01:28:19.960
Oat: I’ll protect you.

01:28:19.960 --> 01:28:21.320
Oat: Nantanan. Just stay here.

01:28:21.320 --> 01:28:22.200
Oat: Just stay like this.

01:28:22.200 --> 01:28:23.000
Daou: Jeff!

01:28:23.440 --> 01:28:24.360
Oat: Calm down.

01:28:24.410 --> 01:28:25.340
Jeff: Up there.

01:28:25.550 --> 01:28:26.440
Oat: Calm down.

01:28:26.580 --> 01:28:30.240
Oat: Nantanan is here. Don't you touch her
because I'm not out yet.

01:28:30.320 --> 01:28:33.720
[Nantatan is well taken care of.]

01:28:34.030 --> 01:28:37.800
Tay: So scary. He looks like
a lion to hunt.

01:28:38.600 --> 01:28:41.730
Oat: This is my real goddess.
I want to protect Nantatan.

01:28:42.040 --> 01:28:43.860
Daou: But the real goddess
has a beautiful voice.

01:28:43.860 --> 01:28:44.900
Oat: Do you sing?

01:28:44.920 --> 01:28:47.620
Nantanan: ♪ Maybe you can see ♪

01:28:47.720 --> 01:28:48.520
Daou: Oh man.

01:28:49.880 --> 01:28:53.080
Nantanan: ♪ Maybe you can see ♪

01:28:53.080 --> 01:28:53.840
Daou: Oh man.

01:28:54.040 --> 01:28:54.680
Oat: Oops.

01:28:54.960 --> 01:28:56.320
Nantanan: I've released an album too.

01:28:56.320 --> 01:29:00.040
Nantanan: P'Tha made an album for me.
Why don't you trust me?

01:29:00.480 --> 01:29:02.200
[Is she a real goddess too?]

01:29:03.080 --> 01:29:04.920
[Do you not trust my goddess?]

01:29:05.800 --> 01:29:06.860
Daou: Brother Tay.

01:29:07.080 --> 01:29:07.880
Daou: Oh no.

01:29:09.560 --> 01:29:10.520
Daou: Come on.

01:29:10.520 --> 01:29:12.720
Daou: Come if you think you can run fast.

01:29:13.000 --> 01:29:14.400
Phuak: Run, Daou, run.

01:29:14.920 --> 01:29:15.900
Jeff: Stop.

01:29:15.960 --> 01:29:16.200
[Jeff comes after hearing the sound.]

01:29:16.200 --> 01:29:17.030
Daou: Come on.

01:29:20.320 --> 01:29:20.960
Daou: Jeff, run!
Jeff, go!

01:29:20.960 --> 01:29:23.760
[The intense attack from
Nantanan, the goddess.]

01:29:24.520 --> 01:29:26.120
Daou: Jeff, run fast. forward.

01:29:26.120 --> 01:29:26.520
Nantanan: I'll go to Jeff.

01:29:26.520 --> 01:29:27.360
[Daou VS Oat]
[Nantanan VS Jeff]

01:29:27.360 --> 01:29:29.320
Daou: Sister Ink. Catch Nantanan.

01:29:32.040 --> 01:29:33.880
Oat: Nantanan, wait! Nantanan!

01:29:33.880 --> 01:29:34.480
[Tay quietly comes to help from behind.]

01:29:34.480 --> 01:29:36.000
[Daou: Trap him.]

01:29:37.080 --> 01:29:37.400
[Ink can't stand it anymore.]

01:29:37.400 --> 01:29:38.920
Daou: Trap him.

01:29:42.560 --> 01:29:44.360
Nantanan: Brother, be careful.

01:29:45.120 --> 01:29:46.080
Nantanan: Brother, be careful.

01:29:46.080 --> 01:29:47.800
Tay: Daou, here, Daou.

01:29:49.200 --> 01:29:50.600
Ink: Brother Tay, hurry.

01:29:54.040 --> 01:29:54.080
Ink: Tay! Hurry up!

01:29:54.080 --> 01:29:56.320
[Spun around twice on the spot]

01:29:56.320 --> 01:29:58.760
[Spun around twice on the spot.
Oat managed to break free]

01:30:00.280 --> 01:30:01.920
[Charging towards Tay
with all his strength]

01:30:02.200 --> 01:30:05.360
Oat: Little deer.

01:30:05.360 --> 01:30:07.840
Oat: Are you lost?

01:30:07.840 --> 01:30:08.840
Tay: Everyone!

01:30:09.640 --> 01:30:13.640
[Gaze locked. Wild bear hunting mode on]

01:30:15.320 --> 01:30:16.120
Tay: Daou!

01:30:19.240 --> 01:30:20.520
[Tay bravely attacks]

01:30:21.240 --> 01:30:23.680
[The wild bear attacks at the same time]

01:30:24.080 --> 01:30:25.600
[Between these two, who will win?]

01:30:34.840 --> 01:30:37.760
[Mentally and physically exhausted]

01:30:38.760 --> 01:30:43.840
[Fought with honor despite defeat]

01:30:44.520 --> 01:30:46.380
Nantanan: Oat, you were amazing.

01:30:47.240 --> 01:30:49.240
Commander R: Tay, out.

01:30:49.240 --> 01:30:50.200
[Tay out]

01:30:50.200 --> 01:30:52.480
Commander R: Tay, out.

01:30:52.880 --> 01:30:55.160
Commander R: Tay, out.

01:30:56.520 --> 01:30:58.520
Commander R: Tay, out.

01:30:59.400 --> 01:31:00.600
Ink: Tay's out?

01:31:01.320 --> 01:31:02.480
Jeff: Tay's out?

01:31:03.560 --> 01:31:04.890
Daou: What should we do?

01:31:06.760 --> 01:31:09.560
Oat: We're going
head to head this time, Nantanan.

01:31:11.000 --> 01:31:11.800
Oat: Come on.

01:31:19.480 --> 01:31:20.720
Daou: If you lose, you lose.

01:31:20.720 --> 01:31:22.160
Ink: Yeah, I couldn't resist anyway.

01:31:22.160 --> 01:31:23.440
Daou: Go fight her.

01:31:25.720 --> 01:31:28.920
[Two goddesses]

01:31:28.920 --> 01:31:32.120
[Two goddesses.
Which one is the real one?]

01:31:32.240 --> 01:31:36.600
[In the end, which team will win?]

01:31:36.760 --> 01:31:40.600
Oat: Come here. Let the girls play
by themselves over there.

01:31:41.840 --> 01:31:42.840
Oat: Come.

01:31:44.360 --> 01:31:46.800
[Jeff the ambusher waits
for a chance to strike from behind]

01:31:47.880 --> 01:31:48.440
Oat: Jeff!

01:31:48.440 --> 01:31:52.280
[Using the wild bear instinct
to block the attack]

01:31:52.440 --> 01:31:53.370
Daou: Catch him!

01:31:54.360 --> 01:31:58.360
[At a disadvantage because
of the two-on-one situation]

01:31:59.840 --> 01:32:01.040
Ink: Daou, watch out!

01:32:01.280 --> 01:32:02.560
Ink: Daou, watch out!

01:32:03.280 --> 01:32:04.480
Ink: Daou, watch out!

01:32:06.040 --> 01:32:08.200
[Was the name tag snatched?]

01:32:10.320 --> 01:32:11.080
Ink: Daou, watch out!

01:32:11.080 --> 01:32:12.000
[Immediate counterattack on Daou]

01:32:12.000 --> 01:32:12.960
Daou: Go, go!

01:32:14.400 --> 01:32:15.000
Ink: Daou, watch out!

01:32:15.000 --> 01:32:15.840
Daou: Go, go!

01:32:16.400 --> 01:32:18.280
[Oat lost his balance from the force
of the tag pull and tripped on a bench]

01:32:22.920 --> 01:32:24.440
Ink: Careful, careful!

01:32:24.440 --> 01:32:24.560
Ink: Be careful, careful.

01:32:24.560 --> 01:32:26.720
[Protecting his name tag
even though he tripped]

01:32:26.720 --> 01:32:28.240
Ink: Be careful, careful.

01:32:30.880 --> 01:32:34.320
[The wild bear's name tag
was firmly torn off by Jeff]

01:32:34.320 --> 01:32:35.640
Jeff: Okay, I got it!

01:32:35.640 --> 01:32:38.520
[Oat out]

01:32:39.000 --> 01:32:39.440
Ink: Be careful, careful.

01:32:39.440 --> 01:32:40.840
[Goddess Nantanan was just
a little too late]

01:32:42.600 --> 01:32:44.060
Jeff: Just tear off Ink's!

01:32:45.920 --> 01:32:47.080
[Great teamwork from Team Ink.
Oat and Nantanan were out in no time]

01:32:47.080 --> 01:32:48.430
Jeff: Tear it off!

01:32:50.760 --> 01:32:53.450
Ink: Nantanan, Nantanan.

01:32:55.520 --> 01:32:57.640
Jeff: Yo, that was awesome.

01:32:58.680 --> 01:33:00.080
Jeff: Well done.

01:33:01.480 --> 01:33:02.680
Commander R: NUi,

01:33:02.880 --> 01:33:03.720
Commander R: Nantanan,

01:33:03.720 --> 01:33:04.200
[The winning team is confirmed]

01:33:04.200 --> 01:33:06.480
Commander R: Oat, out.

01:33:08.360 --> 01:33:09.880
PD: Alright, today's
"Protect the Goddess' Name Tag" mission...

01:33:09.880 --> 01:33:13.800
[It's time to reveal
who the real goddess is.]

01:33:14.560 --> 01:33:17.840
[Which of these two is the real goddess?]

01:33:18.810 --> 01:33:20.610
Ink, Nantanan: Hello everyone.

01:33:22.360 --> 01:33:23.160
Ink: Oh, this.

01:33:23.480 --> 01:33:26.760
[After knowing the result of Charlette,
these two both chose fireworks]

01:33:27.640 --> 01:33:31.520
[If the real goddess is Nantanan = accept punishment.
If the real goddess is Ink = mission success]

01:33:38.400 --> 01:33:39.600
Ink: I'm the real one.

01:33:41.240 --> 01:33:42.760
Ink: I'm the real goddess!

01:33:43.240 --> 01:33:44.720
[Yeah! Yeah!]

01:33:44.720 --> 01:33:45.520
Ink: Okay.

01:33:46.090 --> 01:33:50.640
PD: The final surviving team
is Goddess Ink's team.

01:33:53.720 --> 01:33:55.910
Ink: That's great! Awesome!

01:33:59.400 --> 01:34:01.800
Oat: Do you have anything
you'd like to say?

01:34:01.920 --> 01:34:05.480
Oat: I was too naive. I was blinded
by her beauty from the start of the show.

01:34:05.480 --> 01:34:08.960
Oat: I guess this is a real goddess.
I feel like she has healed me.

01:34:08.960 --> 01:34:10.520
Ink: Then why didn't you believe
Ink was the real one?

01:34:10.520 --> 01:34:11.650
Ink: Am I not pretty?

01:34:11.960 --> 01:34:13.240
Daou: Ink is a bodhisattva.

01:34:13.240 --> 01:34:15.600
Oat: Today, Ink is going with
a Guanyin bodhisattva vibe.

01:34:15.600 --> 01:34:16.640
Charlette: What about me?

01:34:16.640 --> 01:34:18.240
Oat: You're still a kid, kid.

01:34:18.720 --> 01:34:18.860
Daou: But I think it was very interesting.

01:34:18.860 --> 01:34:19.880
[Watch the uncut version of Running Man Thailand
exclusively on the iQIYI app and iQ.com,
the only officially designated streaming platform.]

01:34:19.880 --> 01:34:20.320
Oat: Really?

01:34:20.320 --> 01:34:22.080
Daou: Today, it felt like the three of us
were acting in a TV drama.

01:34:22.080 --> 01:34:22.880
Charlette: Yes.

01:34:22.880 --> 01:34:23.880
Phuak: Tricking each other.

01:34:23.880 --> 01:34:25.130
Charlette: Tricking each other.

01:34:25.130 --> 01:34:27.330
Nantanan: I had faith.

01:34:27.480 --> 01:34:29.250
Nantanan: I firmly believed
I was the goddess.

01:34:29.250 --> 01:34:31.880
Nantanan: That's an actor's duty!

01:34:31.980 --> 01:34:33.240
Phuak: Can you guys clear it up first?

01:34:33.240 --> 01:34:35.370
Phuak: My kids have fallen asleep
waiting for me.

01:34:35.370 --> 01:34:36.770
Phuak: It's already 3am!

01:34:36.930 --> 01:34:38.080
Oat: Your kid is waiting for you
while sleeping, right?

01:34:38.080 --> 01:34:38.720
Phuak: He fell asleep!

01:34:38.720 --> 01:34:41.900
Oat: At this rate every day, even my dog
won't remember I'm its dad.

01:34:41.900 --> 01:34:43.080
Jeff: Okay okay.

01:34:43.160 --> 01:34:48.880
Running Man Thailand, Never Stop Running!

01:34:50.970 --> 01:34:52.000
PD: Today you will compete in
the "Big Eater Monopoly" mission.

01:34:52.000 --> 01:34:54.760
[This round, the competition
is a foodie version of Monopoly]

01:34:55.280 --> 01:34:55.380
That's it.

01:34:55.380 --> 01:34:56.120
[Get to famous eateries
and reclaim survival privileges]

01:34:56.120 --> 01:34:57.180
Where are we going?

01:34:58.560 --> 01:34:59.280
It's not over yet.

01:34:59.280 --> 01:35:02.600
[A fiery eating battle
with survival privileges at stake]

01:35:02.600 --> 01:35:03.760
Let's go look, I'm starving.

01:35:03.760 --> 01:35:06.200
[Which team will have the last laugh?]